dct_title_s: A new map of Europe according to the present general divisions and names of its countries together with their capital cities chief rivers mountains &c.
dct_description_sm: Map of Europe with relief shown pictorially. Plate [4] from: A new sett of maps both of antient and present geography / by Edward Wells. Oxford : Printed at the Theater, 1700.
